        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for information on the slope of ground at Worcester.</p>
            <p>CD’s passion now is worms.</p> 
<p>Sends <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>. While correcting proof, CD remembered an old article by HHJ, which he regrets not including.</p> 
        </abstract>
